## 4. KNOWN HAZARDS (from June 2026 audit)

### Files that MUST NOT ship to production:
- `public/test-admin.html` — DELETE THIS (exposes admin patterns)
- `scratch/` directory — 32 debug scripts, add to .gitignore

### Known domain conflict:
- `sitemap.xml` and `robots.txt` say `khedmetna.tn`
- Everything else says `workedin.tn`
- Until resolved: do NOT create new references to either domain without asking user.

### God components (high regression risk):
- `src/pages/Messages.tsx` — 5,410 lines. Be EXTREMELY careful editing this.
- `src/pages/ContractWorkspacePage.tsx` — complex lifecycle logic.
- When modifying these: make minimal changes, test thoroughly.

### Circular dependency:
- Build has `form-vendor → react-vendor → form-vendor` circular chunk.
- Do NOT add new cross-chunk imports between form/react vendor groups.

### Files with `: any` (tech debt — fix when touching):
- `src/pages/Wallet.tsx`, `src/pages/JobBoard.tsx`, `src/pages/JobDetail.tsx`
- `src/services/jobs.ts`, `src/pages/admin/PaymentsTab.tsx`
- `src/components/settings/ProfileSettings.tsx`

